IMAPAccount mail
Host mail.farley.io
User sean@farley.io
PassCmd "~/.epass.sh https://mail.farley.io sean@farley.io"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2

IMAPStore mail-remote
Account mail

MaildirStore mail-local
Path ~/.mail/
Inbox ~/.mail/inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel mail
Master :mail-remote:
Slave  :mail-local:
Patterns * !virtual*
# Automatically create missing mailboxes, both locally and on the server
Create Both
# Save the synchronization state files in the relevant directory
SyncState *
Expunge Both
CopyArrivalDate yes
